<h3 style="font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">Recipients</h3>
<hr>
<br/>
<p>Recipients can come to this page and search for orders by their name.  This will update the page with all the order lines associated with that particular name.</p>

<form>
	<input type="text" id="recipient" value="Foo Bar">
	<button id="showTable" style="width: 60px; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 4px;">Submit</button>			
</form>

<h3>Orders for Recipient:</h1>
<table>
		<thead>
			<th>Recipient Email</th>
			<th>Gift Card Received</th>
			<th>Quantity</th>
		</thead>
		<tbody>
			<tr>
				<td>{{recipient_email}}</td>
				<td>{{name}}</td>
				<td>{{quantity}}</td>
			</tr>
		</tbody>
</table>
	
